x500.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">This easy 5-ingredient Italian Sausage Bake serves up a rich and hearty family meal with minimal fuss (and minimal dishes)!</figcaption></figure>
