<p>This all-in-one dinner will taste amazing with some <strong><a href="https://bakeitwithlove.com/oven-garlic-bread/">oven garlic bread</a></strong> or <strong><a href="https://bakeitwithlove.com/cast-iron-skillet-garlic-herb-focaccia-bread/">garlic herb focaccia bread</a></strong>. Add a side of <strong><a href="https://bakeitwithlove.com/caesar-salad/">Caesar salad</a></strong> for a simple appetizer, too! Enjoy!</p>



<h2 id="%f0%9f%92%ad-angelas-pro-tips-recipe-notes"   class="wp-block-heading" >💭 Angela's Pro Tips &amp; Recipe Notes</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Great stir-in ideas include</strong> mushrooms, green bell peppers, sweet bell peppers, freshly ground fennel seeds, halved cherry or grape tomatoes, and of course...more cheese!</li>



<li><strong>You can make your casserole ahead of time</strong>, simply prepare it according to the instructions. Cover and refrigerate until ready to bake, then allow a few extra minutes of cooking time.</li>



<li><strong>Pick out your favorite sausage links</strong> from brands like Johnsonville, Premio, Aidells, Applegate Farms, and Swaggerty Farms to make this easy pasta bake!</li>
</ul>



